{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   /calculators — data-driven gallery of every interactive calculator
   on the site.

   ─── Architecture ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
   This page is rendered from `src/_data/explorations.json`. Any entry
   in the registry that carries a `calculator_tile` block gets a tile
   here automatically; entries without that block do not. Adding a new
   calculator to /calculators is therefore a single edit to
   explorations.json — no template changes required.

   The `calculator_tile` schema:

     calculator_tile: {
       tagline:      string  (required)  — 1-line copy, may include
                                            HTML entities (&mdash;,
                                            &rsquo;, etc.)
       preview_kind: "svg" | "live-chart"  (required)
       preview_id:   string              — required if preview_kind ===
                                            "live-chart"; the DOM id
                                            picked up by
                                            calculators-minis.js
                                            (e.g. "mini-retirement")
       anchor:       string  (optional)  — appended to the tile href
                                            after /<slug>.html;
                                            defaults to "#calculator".
                                            Set to "" for pages with no
                                            tab anchor (the-fixed-pie,
                                            the-half-life,
                                            the-melting-ice-cube).
       featured:     boolean (optional)  — true puts the tile in the
                                            top Featured row (large
                                            card, special styling).
                                            Defaults to false.
       position:     integer (required)  — sort key within the page;
                                            featured row is sorted by
                                            position too, so featured
                                            entries should have the
                                            lowest positions
     }

   For svg previews: the icon markup lives at
     src/_includes/components/calc-tile-icons/<slug>.njk
   and is auto-resolved by slug. To add a new svg-preview tile, create
   that file and add the calculator_tile block in explorations.json.

   For live-chart previews: the renderer must already exist in
   src/_includes/_pageassets/calculators-minis.js, wired to the
   `preview_id` via the {id → render-function} map near the bottom of
   that file. Adding a new live-chart preview = add a renderer there
   AND the tile block here.

   ─── History ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   v1 (May 2026): 5-tile text-list.
   v2 (May 2026): polished gallery with 1 live preview (Heatmap) as
                  proof-of-concept.
   v2.5: expanded to 7 live renderers in calculators-minis.js.
   v3 (June 2026): renamed Tools → Calculators (commits 132f79a /
                   0148ba3); Heatmap moved to /the-gallery; Bitcoin
                   Retirement promoted to Featured slot.
   v4 (June 2026, this commit): data-driven from explorations.json's
                   calculator_tile schema. Removed the unused
                   `is_calculator` boolean from the registry — its
                   semantic ("personal-decision tool only") had drifted
                   from the page's actual contents (which include
                   interactive demonstrations like Horizon, Fixed
                   Share, Half-Life, MIC). The `calculator_tile` block
                   replaces it as the single source of truth: presence
                   of the block = tile rendered here.

   ─── Tech debt ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   - SP500_TR_DATA is duplicated between calculators-minis.js and
     bitcoin-vs-the-stock-market.js. Marked 'TR-SYNC' in both files.
     Future cleanup: extract to shared/comparator-data.js.
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}

<main class="calculators-page">

  <header class="calc-hero">
    <h1>Calculators</h1>
    <p class="calc-hero-lede">
      A working gallery of interactive tools to think through bitcoin decisions in your own life &mdash; past, present, and future.
    </p>
  </header>

  {# ═══ FEATURED ROW ════════════════════════════════════════════════
     Tiles with calculator_tile.featured === true, sorted by position.
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
  <section class="calc-row calc-row-featured" aria-labelledby="featured-heading">
    <h2 id="featured-heading" class="calc-row-heading">Featured</h2>

    <div class="calc-tile-grid calc-tile-grid-featured">
      {% for ex in explorations | sortByCalculatorTilePosition %}
        {% if ex.calculator_tile and ex.calculator_tile.featured %}
          {% set ct = ex.calculator_tile %}
          {% set anchor = ct.anchor if ct.anchor is defined else "#calculator" %}
          <a href="/{{ ex.slug }}.html{{ anchor }}" class="calc-tile calc-tile-featured" aria-label="Open {{ ex.title | safe }} calculator">
            <div class="calc-tile-preview">
              {% if ct.preview_kind == "live-chart" %}
                <div id="{{ ct.preview_id }}"></div>
              {% else %}
                {% include 'components/calc-tile-icons/' + ex.slug + '.njk' %}
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="calc-tile-body">
              <h3 class="calc-tile-name">{{ ex.title | safe }}</h3>
              <p class="calc-tile-tagline">{{ ct.tagline | safe }}</p>
              <span class="calc-tile-cta">Open &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  {# ═══ TOOLS GRID ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     All tiles where calculator_tile.featured is not true, sorted by
     position. Order is roughly by user value / decision impact
     (live-chart calculators front, foundational viz toward the back).
     ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
  <section class="calc-row" aria-labelledby="tools-heading">
    <h2 id="tools-heading" class="calc-row-heading">All calculators</h2>

    <div class="calc-tile-grid">
      {% for ex in explorations | sortByCalculatorTilePosition %}
        {% if ex.calculator_tile and not ex.calculator_tile.featured %}
          {% set ct = ex.calculator_tile %}
          {% set anchor = ct.anchor if ct.anchor is defined else "#calculator" %}
          <a href="/{{ ex.slug }}.html{{ anchor }}" class="calc-tile">
            <div class="calc-tile-preview">
              {% if ct.preview_kind == "live-chart" %}
                <div id="{{ ct.preview_id }}"></div>
              {% else %}
                {% include 'components/calc-tile-icons/' + ex.slug + '.njk' %}
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="calc-tile-body">
              <h3 class="calc-tile-name">{{ ex.title | safe }}</h3>
              <p class="calc-tile-tagline">{{ ct.tagline | safe }}</p>
              <span class="calc-tile-cta">Open &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
